@estimate_bill
subtitle: -1 resources
view-if: num_queued_bills > 0

= Read the Room

Your contacts in the chamber can give you a rough sense of how a bill would fare. It will cost you a favour.

Choose a bill to assess:

- @estimate_queued_0: [+ queued_0_label +]
- @estimate_queued_1: [+ queued_1_label +]
- @estimate_queued_2: [+ queued_2_label +]
- @estimate_queued_3: [+ queued_3_label +]
- @estimate_queued_4: [+ queued_4_label +]
- @estimate_queued_5: [+ queued_5_label +]
- @estimate_queued_6: [+ queued_6_label +]
- @estimate_queued_7: [+ queued_7_label +]
- @estimate_queued_8: [+ queued_8_label +]
- @estimate_queued_9: [+ queued_9_label +]


@estimate_queued_0
view-if: num_queued_bills >= 1
on-arrival: {! Q.estimate_target = 0; !}
go-to: run_estimate

@estimate_queued_1
view-if: num_queued_bills >= 2
on-arrival: {! Q.estimate_target = 1; !}
go-to: run_estimate

@estimate_queued_2
view-if: num_queued_bills >= 3
on-arrival: {! Q.estimate_target = 2; !}
go-to: run_estimate

